%% Phase 1 POC — end-to-end incident sequence (ORDER-7842)
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant EXT as Port Advisory Source
    participant EM as Event Mesh
    participant ORCH as Orchestrator Agent
    participant DA as Data Retrieval
    participant AG as Alt Generator
    participant IS_A as Impact Scorer
    participant UI as Joule UI
    participant USR as Supply Chain Head
    participant ISv as Integration Suite

    EXT->>EM: port.advisory event
    EM->>ORCH: trigger
    ORCH->>ORCH: plan (retrieve → assess → generate → score)
    ORCH->>DA: get_order(ORDER-7842)
    DA-->>ORCH: order + customer tier + inventory across entities
    ORCH->>AG: find_alternatives(order, context)
    AG-->>ORCH: 3 options (air-freight, stock transfer, alt supplier)
    ORCH->>IS_A: score(options, weights)
    IS_A-->>ORCH: ranked options with rationale
    ORCH->>UI: present ranked options
    UI->>USR: "Recommend Option A (air-freight, +$22k, on-time)"
    USR->>UI: approve Option A
    UI->>ISv: execute reroute via governed API
    ISv-->>UI: confirmation logged
